{"tid":1597712,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有嘢一齊講有街一齊出（WhatsApp group)","createTime":"2019-09-27T05:22:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T01:14:13.000Z","uid":9178,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f92e7ada82f4226c6cae748e9a7379b71d9f9fe6","tid":1597712,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:22:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個谷開咗一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個專屬於大家既Whatsapp谷<br />\n係咪覺得返工<br />\n返學無聊日日起身之後都好似無乜目標咁<br />\n就係因為你地未加入我地呢個吹水谷<br />\n如果想傾計、吹水、hea時間、識下人，我地就好適合啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想出街 唔洗再怕自己一個 出聲呀 一齊起行<br />\n大家嚟個互相照應<br />\n日常食飯玩樂都無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不限年齡性別，只要有心吹水，一切都歡迎<br />\n歡迎join us<br />\n唔怕Dead Air，只怕你唔上水<br />\n加入我地啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/1E3dXd8VvjeUwCrn9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F1E3dXd8VvjeUwCrn9&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=e28f7366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/1E3dXd8VvjeUwCrn9</a>"},{"pid":"78b258b5f100f44baf56e6a3c67624bf7d0df87e","tid":1597712,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />望各兄弟安全"},{"pid":"b8564048753d8d55805165601d90e4c5c0649e95","tid":1597712,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e0bd477133764b7757342de8826987c01edf13","tid":1597712,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8fce3b58208854808d7eaacb7f2c35526a6701","tid":1597712,"uid":96195,"like":0,"d